WHY DO BAND??

Band is a great activity for so many reasons! Here are a few of them:


Studies show that students who learn an instrument:

Gain increased cognitive abilities Gain increased motor skills

Build reasoning skills

And do better academically than students who do not practice an instrument Read the studies HERE.


Playing an instrument uses the WHOLE BRAIN.


Band is fun!!!
